urls.title: Delta Air Lines SkyMiles Shopping: Shop Online & Earn Miles
urls.description: Earn miles when you shop online at 1,000+ popular stores. Find coupons & promo codes to save even more. Turn your online shopping into more miles today.

data.text:
@Delta

https://t.co/sZofm2JusS 

Login with your loyalty program number & select the stores you want to shop at. It will show you how many miles per $ at each store
Download the plugin & then wherever you're shopping it will tell you if you can earn miles & if they have coupons!
